{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2010-08-26-moyashimon-review/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"少年读书隙中窥月"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9833ec58-8cf6-577a-b112-32b24f4c63ce","excerpt":"…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2f26799174d75ccdef864553c0c5ae18/c08c5/4558069_12828016829.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4558069 12828016829\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/2f26799174d75ccdef864553c0c5ae18/1c72d/4558069_12828016829.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2f26799174d75ccdef864553c0c5ae18/a80bd/4558069_12828016829.jpg 148w,\n/static/2f26799174d75ccdef864553c0c5ae18/1c91a/4558069_12828016829.jpg 295w,\n/static/2f26799174d75ccdef864553c0c5ae18/1c72d/4558069_12828016829.jpg 590w,\n/static/2f26799174d75ccdef864553c0c5ae18/c08c5/4558069_12828016829.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>《もやしもん》，译名为豆芽小文或者萌菌物语，讲述的是一位看得见细菌的少年和他的伙伴在东京农大的欢乐生活。在当中也穿插了关于细菌的科普知识。这部动画实在是很有意思，人物都极具性格，出现的细菌也很萌很可爱。在片中表现出来的日本的农工大学的风景更也让我感觉新奇有趣。自己评价这部作品属于中上，在推荐之列。</p>\n<p>值得一提的是本片的实景 OP 做得十分之精致。用三维动画做出来的萌菌和实景融合得非常地好，OP 中出现了玻璃、光滑金属表面等材质，而得益于优秀的图形技术，该反射的的地方都做得很到位。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"《もやしもん》简评","publish_date":"2010-08-26T13:42:16.000+08:00","revise_date":"2010-08-26T13:42:16.000+08:00","draft":false}}},"pageContext":{"previous":{"id":"52a846c1-42d8-5bbb-bc2b-ae53a8a35243","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2010-08-22-prof-layton-and-the-eternal-diva-review/","type":"blog","timeToRead":{"words":285,"minutes":2}},"frontmatter":{"title":"《雷顿教授与永远的歌姬》简评","publish_date":"2010-08-22T00:37:16.000+08:00"}},"slug":"/blog/2010-08-26-moyashimon-review/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1330398833","2356112386"],"slicesMap":{}}